fill\"></i>Fenced enclosures</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Open grass areas</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Agility equipment</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Water stations</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Waste disposal</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Best For</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-list\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">High-energy dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Social dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Owners looking for free exercise options</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What to Bring</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-list\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Leash (for entering/exiting)</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Water bowl</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Waste bags</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Toys</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Treats</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Pro Tips</h4><ul class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d tips-list\"><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Check park rules before visiting</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Keep your dog&#x27;s vaccinations up to date</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Supervise your dog at all times</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Clean up after your dog immediately</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Respect other dogs and owners</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-footer\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d expand-toggle\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">View guide</span><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></button><a class=\"jump-link\" href=\"#dog-park-parks\">Jump to list<i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></a></div></article></div></section></div></div></section><section id=\"map-and-neighborhoods\" class=\"map-experience-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Interactive planning</span><h2>See everything laid out on the map</h2><p>Use the live map to lock in nearby options, preview ratings, and save time hopping between neighborhoods.</p></div><div class=\"map-grid\"><div class=\"map-panel\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div style=\"min-height:320px;background:#f3f4f6\"></div><!--/$--></div><div class=\"map-sidebar\"><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Quick filters</h3><div class=\"map-chip-grid\"><button type=\"button\"><span>Dog Park</span><small>3</small></button></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Highest-rated nearby</h3><div class=\"mini-park-list\"><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Our Home Dog Boarding</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>5.0</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Villa La PAWS</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.8</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>The Groomer&#x27;s In LLC</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.4</strong></div></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card muted\"><p>Tip: tap any map marker to open directions, amenities, and current open hours.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"planning-essentials\" class=\"planning-essentials-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Visit toolkit</span><h2>Plan the perfect dog outing in <!-- -->Maple Shade</h2><p>Borrow best practices from local trainers, rangers, and experienced pet parents.</p></div><div class=\"planning-grid\"><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h3>Peak &amp; quiet windows</h3><ul><li>6–9 AM: high energy social hour</li><li>10 AM–3 PM weekdays: calm training-friendly window</li><li>After 4 PM: sunset crowd + cooler temps</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-backpack\"></i></div><h3>Essentials checklist</h3><ul><li>Leash + harness for entry/exit control</li><li>Collapsible water bowl and fresh water</li><li>Plenty of waste bags and high-value treats</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-shield-check\"></i></div><h3>Local regulations</h3><ul><li>Keep proof of vaccinations or city license handy</li><li>Voice control required in most off-leash zones</li><li>Limit three dogs per handler in public parks</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-heart\"></i></div><h3>Community etiquette</h3><ul><li>Scan the park before entering and remove prong collars</li><li>Monitor play styles and intervene early</li><li>Share shaded space and refill water when you&#x27;re done</li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id=\"owner-cta\" class=\"owner-cta-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Partner with us</span><h2>Feature your Maple Shade dog park</h2><p>Upgrade to a featured listing, share live availability, or pitch a new indoor concept. Our team drives qualified local pet parents every week.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List a property</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Contact the team</a></div></div></section><section id=\"park-directory\" class=\"park-directory-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">City directory</span><h2>All dog parks in <!-- -->Maple Shade</h2><p>Filter-ready cards with ratings, amenities, and quick actions. Use the chips to jump between sections.</p></div><div class=\"category-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\">Dog Park</button></div><div id=\"dog-park-parks\" class=\"directory-category\"><div class=\"directory-header\"><div><h3>Dog Park<!-- -->s<!-- --> in <!-- -->Maple Shade</h3><p>3<!-- --> locations ·<!-- --> <!-- -->4.7<!-- --> <!-- -->average rating</p></div><span class=\"directory-count\">3</span></div><div class=\"directory-grid\"><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/our-home-dog-boarding\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Our Home Dog Boarding</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 7:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Maple Shade<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Serious about your pup&#x27;s fitness and focus? Our Home Dog Boarding in [Maple Shade](/cities/maple-shade-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 5 stars by a community of 14 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of &quot;constructive play.&quot; It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\n\nThe layout at Our Home Dog Boarding is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](http://ourhomedogboarding.com/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/the-groomer-s-in-llc\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">The Groomer&#x27;s In LLC</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens Saturday at 8:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Maple Shade<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">The Groomer&#x27;s In LLC has become a favorite among the area residents.  What makes this dog facility special is its clean, spacious, attentive. The staff&#x27;s dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. clean and well-maintained facilities This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (856) 779-1903. </p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/villa-la-paws\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Villa La PAWS</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 7:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Maple Shade<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Serious about your pup&#x27;s fitness and focus? Villa La PAWS in [Maple Shade](/cities/maple-shade-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.8 stars by a community of 151 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of &quot;constructive play.&quot; It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\n\nThe layout at Villa La PAWS is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](http://villalapawsnj.com/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"nearby-cities\" class=\"nearby-cities-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Explore the region</span><h2>Dog parks near <!-- -->Maple Shade</h2><p>Worth the drive? Check out top-rated indoor parks in neighboring cities.</p></div><div class=\"nearby-cities-grid\" style=\"displa